						"title": "Cloudflare API Shield",
						"subtitle": null,
						"copy": "### Organizations must not only protect APIs that drive business but also easily manage and monitor them.  \n\nToday Cloudflare API Shield, now generally available, keeps APIs secure and productive.  We'll soon add API management and monitoring to make API Shield a full API Gateway so businesses can create, manage and secure APIs: \n\n- Create and manage APIs directly with Cloudflare Workers \n- Automatically detect unmanaged APIs (ready today with API Shield)\n- Address authentication and authorization\n- Identify and stop API abuse (ready today with API Shield)\n- Transform, route, log, and measure API requests\n\n### Contact Cloudflare to activate API Shield now and expect additional gateway functionality to come soon.",
